Input: Raw transaction bytes → disassembled opcodes + data
Tokenization: 
- Opcodes: PUSH1, CALL, MSTORE, etc. (256 tokens)
- Addresses: 0xabc... → ADDR_0xabc (20 bytes → 1 token)  
- Values: 1e18 → NUM_1e18 (log-scaled)
- Events: Transfer, Approval → EVENT_TRANSFER

Model: GPT-style causal transformer
- 124M params (trainable from scratch)
- Unsupervised on normal txs only
- No attack labels needed